# Project Configuration

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15
- React 19
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion
- Lucide React
- shadcn/ui
- Supabase (Backend)

## Critical Patterns & Conventions
- **Mobile First**: All components must be designed for mobile first.
- **Atomic Commits**: Each change should be self-contained and logical.
- **Type Safety**: Use TypeScript for all components and utilities.
- **Clean Code**: Prioritize readability and maintainability.
- **Consistency**: Use the defined color palette and typography.
